The paper deals with language identification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves data analysis and classification, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of neural networks and optimization techniques could also suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible sub-category.
